node.title: Victoria has recorded 1,069 new local COVID-19 cases and two deaths
node.alt: A sign about vaccination with a crowd of people in the background.
node.description: There are now 11,393 active cases of the virus in Victoria, and 597 people have died during the current Delta outbreak.
node.content:
["Victoria has recorded 1,069\u00a0new local COVID-19 cases and two\u00a0deaths.\u00a0", "There are now 11,393\u00a0active cases of the virus in Victoria, and 597\u00a0people have died during the current Delta outbreak.\u00a0", "There are 310\u00a0people in hospital with the virus in Victoria, of whom 74\u00a0are in intensive care and 37\u00a0are on a ventilator.", "The health department said a further 41\u00a0people are in ICU but their infections are no longer considered active.", "The new cases were detected from 67,312\u00a0test results received yesterday.", "There were 2,357\u00a0doses of vaccine administered at state-run sites yesterday, as well as more vaccinations at GP clinics and other venues.", "More to come.", "", "
